{"action":"created","issue":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/51466","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/51466/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/51466/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/51466/events","html_url":"https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/pull/51466","id":1913842900,"node_id":"PR_kwDOABkWpM5bP8o2","number":51466,"title":"Stop running finalizers on exit","user":{"login":"kpamnany","id":3784427,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjM3ODQ0Mjc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3784427?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/kpamnany","html_url":"https://github.com/kpamnany","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kpamnany/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kpamnany/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kpamnany/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kpamnany/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kpamnany/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kpamnany/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kpamnany/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kpamnany/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kpamnany/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"labels":[{"id":1363386,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwxMzYzMzg2","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/labels/breaking","name":"breaking","color":"800000","default":false,"description":"This change will break code"},{"id":195227131,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwxOTUyMjcxMzE=","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/labels/GC","name":"GC","color":"009800","default":false,"description":"Garbage collector"},{"id":294535982,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwyOTQ1MzU5ODI=","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/labels/needs%20docs","name":"needs docs","color":"cc26b5","default":false,"description":"Documentation for this change is required"},{"id":421481488,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWw0MjE0ODE0ODg=","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/labels/needs%20news","name":"needs news","color":"d4c5f9","default":false,"description":"A NEWS entry is required for this change"}],"state":"open","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":21,"created_at":"2023-09-26T16:03:49Z","updated_at":"2023-10-02T16:19:14Z","closed_at":null,"author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","active_lock_reason":null,"draft":false,"pull_request":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/pulls/51466","html_url":"https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/pull/51466","diff_url":"https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/pull/51466.diff","patch_url":"https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/pull/51466.patch","merged_at":null},"body":"Closes #50038.

We've observed that when GC is triggered during exit, Julia can freeze during stop-the-world. This is a symptom of a general problem with running finalizers at exit -- program threads are still running and the various live objects are potentially in use. Pausing threads before running finalizers would possibly introduce other problems.

For this reason, as observed below, other languages (Java, .NET, Go) do not run finalizers on exit and with this PR, Julia will also stop running finalizers on exit.","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/51466/reactions","total_count":2,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":2,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/51466/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null},"comment":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/comments/1743321286","html_url":"https://github.com/JuliaLang/julia/pull/51466#issuecomment-1743321286","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/JuliaLang/julia/issues/51466","id":1743321286,"node_id":"IC_kwDOABkWpM5n6PjG","user":{"login":"kpamnany","id":3784427,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjM3ODQ0Mjc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3784427?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/kpamnany","html_url":"https://github.com/kpamnany","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kpamnany/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kpamnany/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kpamnany/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kpamnany/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kpamnany/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kpamnany/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kpamnany/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kpamnany/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/kpamnany/received_events","type":"User","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2023-10-02T16:19:14Z","updated_at":"2023-10-02T16:19:14Z","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","body":"Updated PR description above. Removed `jl_gc_run_all_finalizers()` and `schedule_all_finalizers()`. Removed references to `jl_gc_run_all_finalizers()` from the documentation. Added a brief n